column5: We have a Houseboat trip out of Sioux Narrows planned for week of 14th - 23rd of Sept this year... Does anyone have any HOT tips or ideas for Walleyes and Pike? I.E. location, depth, tactics and areas? I realize the weather factor will determine much of this, but I thought maybe someone out there has some experience in this location of LOW. Coming in from Denver, so you see wer'e travelling a distance... Thanks, Jim R. P.S. Thanks for the info Darcy!
Hey Jim I you want e-mail just before you come, and I will give you and idea of what going.[email protected]
